data.description: Rare opportunity to buy a log home on the lake in Lakemont Colony with creek on side of property. This 2 bedroom, 2 bath home could be (in this agents opinion) set up and be a 3 bedroom home. The main cabin was built in 1998 and then added onto in 2008. It features a METALROOF, SCREENED PORCH, DECK OVERLOOKING THE WATERFALL/CREEK, SCREENED HOT TUB all nestled in the woods in Lakemont Colony on the LAKE! 2 car carport with workshop. The living room features a WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE with STONE HEARTH,VAULTED CEILING, BAR AREA & BUILT-IN BOOKCASES. The master suite features closet with laundry area tucked in. The foundation has walk-in area with storage. Use this as your GET-AWAY or FULL TIME RESIDENCE, either way you will look forward to coming home to this gorgeous property.
